import React, { useEffect } from 'react'
import { Button, Card, CardContent, TextField, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import { Box } from '@mui/system'
import Center from './Center'

export default function Login() {
  return (
    <form noValidate>
      <TextField 
      label="Email"
      name="email"
      variant="outlined" />
      <TextField 
      label="Password"
      name="password"
      variant="outlined" />


    </form>
  )
}
